  <h2>the problem ‚úçÔ∏è</h2>
  <p>The core problem I am trying to solve with <a target=‚Äù_blank‚Äù style="text-decoration: underline;" href="http://www.fontsinthewild.com/">fonts in the wild </a>is the challenge of finding quality, free fonts. I spoke with many designers and developers who struggle to find free type inspiration. Current resources, such as Typewolf focus on expensive fonts with no option to filter through accessible options.</p>
