<section class="decisions">
  <%= image_tag("fitwmm.jpg", class: "covid1") %>
  <div class="finding" style="align-self: center">
    <%= image_tag("marker-1.svg") %>
    <p>The filter options clearly demonstrate the value proposition of finding quality, open source fonts for both commercial and personal design work. I chose to create a Pinterest like feed with rounded playful corners and infinite scroll to encourage browsing for inspiration, keeping the frame narrow to maximize scannability. I added links to the websites on the home to minimize the amount of clicks to view the original design.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="finding2 finding" style="align-self: center">
    <%= image_tag("fitwmark.svg") %>
    <p>I chose to include a "you might also like" algorithm to quickly find similar font inspiration. I also chose to show the details of the post in a modal to quickly click left and right through modals and click out to continue scrolling.</p>
  </div>
  <%= image_tag("modal.jpg", class: "covid2") %>
</section>
<section class="problem">
  <h2>what i've <br>learned üìö</h2>
